@using System.Web.Mvc;

@helper Script(string scriptName, UrlHelper url)
{
    <script src="@url.Content("../../Scripts/" + scriptName)" type="text/javascript"></script>
}

@*

The static methods do not have access to the Url.Content. So you will have to use the UrlHelper type
parameter to invoke the .Content.

Now to use it, use @Content.Script(..., Url) instead of simply @Script(..)
*@